Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.16,0:00:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前情提要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被袭击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've been attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.13,0:00:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How does that make you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.71,0:00:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感到害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.17,0:00:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在我们在表面上 最应该展现的是力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which is why the best face we can project outward now is one of strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.05,0:00:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你做了什么  -你不能留在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-What have you done? -You can't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别反抗 保持冷静 你可以呼吸的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't fight it. Keep calm. You can breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.72,0:00:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的黎明刚醒来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The new Dawn, just awoken.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.85,0:00:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-有什么不对劲 -出了什么问题吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Something's wrong. -Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.77,0:00:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有种奇怪的感觉 我去边界附近走走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just a weird feeling. I'm gonna walk the perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些可是护卫舰 武装飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those are corvettes. Gunships.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.65,0:00:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通讯浮标没有回应 失去信号了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Comms buoy's not responding. It's gone dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.61,0:00:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定与穹窿有关 空域正在扩大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's gotta be connected to the Vault. The null field's expanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天 安纳克里昂人就出现了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the very next day, the Anacreons showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.24,0:01:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（改编自艾萨克阿西莫夫的小说）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经有一个男人 拜访哈里谢顿 请他告知自己的命运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Once, a man came to Hari Seldon and asked to be told his fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He wanted to know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预测模型是否能测量他人生的重要性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}whether the predictive models could chart the significance of his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但哈里告诉他 只有一群人的行为能被预测\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But Hari told him only the movements of masses could be predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,个人的命运将永远是一个谜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The fate of one individual will always remain a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文明的构造\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The clockwork of civilization…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化的兴起与消亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the rise and fall of cultures…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.19,0:03:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因果与世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}causes and worlds…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于这些问题 哈里谢顿早已解开谜底\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These were answers Hari Seldon had long since unriddled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信仰是一种强大的武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Belief is a powerful weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:04:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此 帝国才这么忌惮哈里的预测\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's why the Empire feared Hari Seldon's predictions so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大帝们统治着世俗事物 但身后事呢 我们的灵魂呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Empires govern worldly concerns, but what comes after? Our souls?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些属于信仰范畴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These realms are the purview of faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而信仰是在永恒之火中铸造的宝剑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And faith is a sword forged in the fires of the infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大帝 你需要换种娱乐吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Empire? Do you seek different amusement?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就足够了 常规的方式、常规的欢愉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll do. For the routine pleasures in the routine manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢哪种欢愉 大帝 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which pleasures do you prefer, Empire?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能提供虚无的欢愉吗 那有可能吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you offer the pleasure of nothing? Is that on the menu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说的是真的吗 谁都不能碰你 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it true? No one's allowed to touch you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的胆子挺大的啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bold, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只有24个小时来服侍你 我想好好利用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have only 24 hours of service to you. I want to make the most of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你试一下触摸我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then try to touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让你试一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said try.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光环能阻挡动能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The aura repels kinetic energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再试一次 这一次动作轻柔一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want you to try it again, with a softer touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Slower.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Slower.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, how…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他部分呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}…does the rest work?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事需要你务必出席 大帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are required, Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白大帝此刻有肢体亲密接触的需求\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand Empire has a physiological need for intimacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但当前事宜的重要性超出这一需求\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the current matter supersedes this need.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使者赞沃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ambassador Thanwall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至高无上的大帝 荣耀之光…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Most esteemed Empire, glory to the light--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话直说吧 使者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Out with it, Ambassador.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比邻星教宗欧珀去世了 大帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Proxima Opal has passed, Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节哀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our condolences.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节哀 真诚致哀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Condolences. Heartfelt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 大帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比邻星教宗欧珀的教众将怀念及哀悼她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Proxima Opal will be missed and mourned by her flock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主教团将提拔她的继任者玛泽菲尔格拉特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now the conclave will elevate her successor, Zephyr Gilat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位有能力的候选人 我们喜欢她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A capable candidate. We like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使者 请转达我们的哀悼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Carry our condolences forward, Ambassador.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并告知格拉特 川陀永远欢迎她的来临\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And inform Gilat she's always welcome on Trantor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于继任者 大帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On the topic of a successor, Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在一些争议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there is some debate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一位候选人的呼声颇高\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Another candidate has been gaining support.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽菲尔哈利玛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Zephyr Halima.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利玛伊法不遵从既成的教规\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Halima Ifa does not adhere to accepted doctrine,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与过去的比邻星教宗不同\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as have our previous proximas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她倡导回到《元八开经》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She is advocating for a return to the Primary Octavo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是自寻死路吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is she suicidal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这女人是谁 胆敢质疑我们的根基 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who is this woman to question our primacy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请恕罪 大帝 我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A-A-Apologies, Empire. I-I--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你知道这事吗  -刚刚才知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Did you know about this? -Only moments ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧珀的葬礼是什么时候 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When is Opal's funeral?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两天后 大帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two days hence, Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要对他人提及今天的对话 我们很快会联系你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Say nothing of this conversation. We will contact you shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前任比邻星教宗上位时 是我提供了帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I helped install the previous Proxima.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽快去和主教团见面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll leave for the conclave as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有必要吗 你不能用全息影像联络 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that really necessary? Can't you just holo-cast yourself in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透光教有三万亿教徒 这次教会分裂需要我亲身处理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Luminism claims three trillion followers. This schism requires a personal touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《元八开经》是什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's the Primary Octavo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是异教徒的经文 帝国前时代的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A heretical scripture. Pre-imperial.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它将灵魂与个人知觉连结起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It directly links the soul to individuated sentience.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那是什么… -个人知觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-What does that mean-- -Individuated sentience.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考 黎明兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Think, Brother Dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果灵魂仅与一个独立个体有关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If a soul cleaves only to an individual being,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么人们会质疑没有个体性的事物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that calls into question that which cannot be individuated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有克里昂大帝 都是一世的完美基因复刻品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All Cleons are perfect genetic copies of the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:09:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And therefore…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有灵魂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't have souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这个叫哈利玛的女人是说我们…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, this Halima woman is saying we're, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人性 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not human?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,间接的意思是这样 但…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Indirectly. But--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果星系的民众开始认为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if the galaxy comes to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领袖不如他们 而不是比他们更优越\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}their leaders are less than, rather than more than themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民众也许不会再追随帝国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they may cease to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是一艘玻璃船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are a glass vessel…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由一只灵巧的手控制\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}spun with a fine hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果内部压力开始紊乱并且我们不团结\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the pressures inside start to swirl and we are not uniform…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也许会爆炸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we may burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你是谁  -塞佛哈定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Who are you? -Salvor Hardin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,端点星的守卫者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Warden of Terminus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安纳克里昂人不得进入帝国的领土\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anacreons aren't allowed on imperial soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来这里做什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拾荒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Scrapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很少看见拾荒者披盔戴甲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a lot of armor for scrappers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在找这艘船的导航模组\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're looking for the ship's navigation module.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘废船上的任何关键部件 早在数十年前就被拆走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any critical components were stripped from this hulk decades ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过一位真正的拾荒者会知道这点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, again, a real scrapper would know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该离开 趁帝国还未得知此事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should leave. Before the Empire catches wind of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我族人并不畏惧帝国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My people do not fear the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 你们没想到会碰到我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I caught you by surprise
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你们在临时想办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and now you're improvising.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你们要杀我 你们早就动手了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if you were gonna kill me, you would have already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的计划是 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what's the play?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座塔 带我们去那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That tower. Take us there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是说清吧 守卫者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me be clear, Warden.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道如何利用一切可用的资源\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We know how to use every resource we come across.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们早前观察那几个孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The children we observed earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们看到他们在黎明前夕偷偷溜走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we've seen how they sneak away just before dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远离了你们其他人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}straying far away from the rest of your flock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.69,0:12:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不带我们去那座塔 我们只需利用其中一个孩子就行 很简单\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you won't lead us to the tower, we'll simply utilize one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那么简单 那里有围栏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not that simple. We have a fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道你们有围栏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're aware of your fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们看到你之前在那里进行维护工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We saw you perform maintenance on it earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你是带我们穿越围栏的完美人选\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which makes you the perfect person to take us through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去塔那里吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To the tower then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在围栏上使用了基因识别技术\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The fence uses DNA recognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何不在数据库里的人都会被辐射击中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It'll radiate anyone who isn't in the database.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以带一个人进去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I might be able to get one of you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们一起穿越\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we walk through together,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,围栏会将第二人视作系统错误\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the fence should write off the second person as an error.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就带我们所有人进去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then take us all through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这招只能用一次 可能吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This only works once. Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我过去曾拖进围栏的生物已经死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The only thing I've ever dragged through this fence was already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能感到你的紧张 别紧张\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can feel you tensing up. Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她在这一轮值班结束前没回来 我们会夷平你的城市\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If she isn't back within a watch, we'll raze your city to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去 叫上其他人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go. Get the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建立一个防线 别让人看见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Establish a perimeter and stay out of sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来驾驶 我拿枪 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wanna drive and I'll hold the gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:13:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少告诉我你的名字吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me your name, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们成了好朋友了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are we best friends now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你冒很大的险来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've risked a lot coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们赌上了一切 守卫者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've risked everything, Warden.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不 前方路上有个男孩 -别耍花招 我有眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-No. There was a boy in our path! -Don't get cute. I have eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔在那边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The tower's that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.92,0:14:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是捷径 这条路的守卫比较少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm taking a shortcut. Fewer watchmen this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于塞佛哈定的那些传说  通常从这里开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The stories about Salvor Hardin? They usually begin here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守卫者与幽灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The warden and the ghost,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人费解地紧密联系在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}inexplicably bound together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是怎么避开我们的雷达的 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did they slip past our radar?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是按低空航线飞进来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Flew in the nap of the earth. Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有他们飞船的踪迹吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any sign of their ships?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们自称为拾荒者 说他们在找导航模组\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They claimed to be scrappers. Said they were after a navigation module.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-明显的谎言 -我们必须联络帝国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Obviously bullshit. -We need to contact the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未经授权 我们不能做任何事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't do anything without authorization.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 妈妈 我们只是名义上的帝国哨站\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, Mom. We're an imperial outpost in name only.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们上一次联络我们是哪年哪月  十年前了吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When was the last time they even contacted us? A decade ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不会保护我们的 我们必须自己来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They won't defend us. We need to do it ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别急 暴力是无能者…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Easy. Violence is the last refuge--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的庇护所 我知道 那是老人之言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of the incompetent, I know. That's an old man's doctrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我比你更年轻时观察所得的道理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's an observation I made when I was younger than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哈里的计划中 我们会等待帮助还是独立行动 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would Hari's plan have assumed we'd wait for help or act on our own?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里已经不在这了 妈妈 我们必须自救\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hari is not here, Mom. We need to help ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎醒来 我的好朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome back, best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正要加深对彼此的了解时你就昏迷了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You left the conversation just as we were really getting to know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头疼 感觉牙齿要掉了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Headache? Teeth feel like they're falling out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那该死的东西是什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What was that cursed thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们对端点星殖民时它就在了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was here when we colonized Terminus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在扫描时没探测到它 我猜你们也没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Didn't show up on any of our scans. I guess it didn't show up on yours either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你没有受影响 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why did it not affect you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能说我是你在端点星上最不想碰到的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's just say I'm the last person on Terminus you wanted to come across.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢 守卫者 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what now, Warden?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她带了一支小规模军队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She had a small army with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有他们的脚印 有的很深\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An-- And their tracks, some of them were deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步幅较短 好像他们在搬运沉重的设备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shorter stride lengths. As if they were carrying heavy equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们似乎计划在此驻留 爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like they're planning on digging in, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你想怎么做  -不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Well, what do you wanna do? -I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直遵从我的直觉 但…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've been following my instincts, and--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 也许那只是碰巧走运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know, maybe it was just dumb luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的直觉不仅仅带你上了飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your instincts didn't just lead you to the ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且让你找到了她 你阻止了她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They led you to her. And you stopped her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你数学更好的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you were better at math,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就会知道反复而来的运气 就绝不仅是运气 塞佛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you'd know that repeated luck was more than just luck, Salvor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论你母亲是否愿意承认\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whether your mother wants to admit it or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从你学会走路起 我们一直跟着你的行为做事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we have been following your lead from the moment you pulled yourself upright.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:17:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们选你担任守卫者是有原因的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's no accident the people made you warden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 带领我们吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So lead us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很荣幸初次见到您 大帝 有何可为您效劳 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have never had the pleasure, Empire. How may I be of service?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是欧布雷特队长 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Captain Obrecht, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阴影师 大帝 阴影师欧布雷特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shadowmaster, Empire. Shadowmaster Obrecht.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常相像\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A fine likeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处理有问题的宫殿人员 规程是什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's the protocol for dealing with a problem palace attendant?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问是哪个级别的人员 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What level of attendant, if I may ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-在花园工作的人 -我能问是哪类问题吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Someone who works in the garden. -May I ask the nature of the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能 我只需要她的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You may not. I just want her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题 大帝 若还需要什么 也可以交代我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can ascertain that, Empire. Along with anything else you may require.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时只有这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's all for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到围栏外至少有十几个安纳克里昂人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw at least a dozen Anacreons outside the fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特拉维克 从南边的环圈靠近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Travik, take the southern loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯林 你负责西边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kalin, cover the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶特 你守在东边 监控有没有人从那个山脊过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yate, I want you on the east so you can spot anyone coming over that ridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果看到那些人 我们该做什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if we see any of these guys, what are we supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别向他们开枪 别跟他们说话 观察他们 随时向我汇报情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't shoot at them, don't speak to them. Just watch 'em and keep me informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-端点星出现安纳克里昂人是怎么回事  -她叫法拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-What's this about Anacreons on Terminus? -Calls herself Phara.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外 她的故事完全说不通\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beyond that, nothing about her story adds up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最擅长看出别人是否在撒谎了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If anyone can tell whether somebody's lying, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题就是这个 我看不出她在撒谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's just the thing. I can't tell if she's lying
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不说实情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or if she's just not telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两者有差别吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there a difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个计划 但我需要你的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've got a plan. But I'm gonna need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是做什么 虐囚 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's this? Torture?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的男仆从\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's my manservant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为我跑腿 在需要的时候帮我的靴子封边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Runs and fetches. Reseals my boots when they need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜对我野外的同伴来说 这一轮值班已经结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm thinking a watch has passed, as far as my weald-men are concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底为何来这里 法拉 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why are you really here, Phara?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞佛很擅长读人心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Salvor has a talent for reading people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准得吓人 我刚才还和她母亲聊起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's uncanny, really. I was just telling her mother about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:18:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不相信你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She doesn't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚告诉她你是我的上司 这下我像在拍马屁了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you told her you're my boss. Now my praise rings hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对基地塔为何感兴趣 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's your interest in the Foundation Tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为模组 我已经告诉你了 你总是问我相同的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The module. I already told you. You keep asking me the same questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在给你机会 让你回答得更好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm giving you a chance to give better answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Crowns.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你在找别的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you're after something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有任何安纳克里昂文物 也没有重型武器 所以到底…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't have any Anacreon artifacts, no heavy weapons, so what--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在原地绕圈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is going in circles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解释给她听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Explain it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她想要的给她吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just give her what she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的口音不算糟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your accent's not terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你显然是向港口城市的人学的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were taught by someone in the port city, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懒元音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those lazy vowels.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是贸易商\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm a trader.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶尔与你们星球的人做生意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do business with your people now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得从你身上 我嗅到了狄斯比斯人的味道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thought I smelled a whiff of Thespin on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要导航模组 仅此而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want the navigation module. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是一个谎言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Another lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也说安纳克里昂语 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You speak Anacreon as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个字都不懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-但你知道我在撒谎  -反面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Yet you know I'm lying? -Cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,概率是二分之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That was a 50-50 chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:19:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是反面 你到底是谁 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cats again. Who are you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,概率是四分之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Twenty-five percent chance there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又回到正面了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now it's back to crowns.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八分之一了 又一个正面 你为什么来这里 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Twelve and a half percent. And another crown. Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是正面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Another crown again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以把概率告诉你 但是反复而来的运气绝不是运气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd give you the percentage, but repeated luck is never luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是拾荒者 为找模组而来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're scrappers. The module.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是拾荒者 导航模组不过是为了转移…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not scrappers. And the navigation module's a distraction--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再玩这些幼稚的把戏了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Enough of these child games.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个狄斯比斯暴徒的链子解开 让他直接动手吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take this Thespin thug off his leash and let him get on with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的疤痕…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your scars…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟹足肿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}keloids.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的左眼…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your left eye…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳米玻璃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}nano-glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:21:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在帝国轰炸安纳克里昂时 失去左眼的吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You lose it when the Empire bombed Anacreon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当时应该是五、六岁 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I imagine you must have been, what, five, six at the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中子弹的爆发力较低 但是电离辐射的能量很高\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Neutron bombs have a low explosive yield but a high amount of ionizing radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道大约一半的人口一周内就死去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, I know about 50% of the population died off within a week,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外的两、三成人在那一年里死去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}another 20 or 30 within the remaining year.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很可能在那次轰炸后 成为孤儿了 对吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Odds are you came out the other end an orphan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许失去了爸妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Probably lost a mom and dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活活地被烧死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Boiled alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是慢性死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or maybe s-slower.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.60,0:21:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,癌症\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的母亲是甲状腺癌 她的嗓音在死前变了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thyroid for your mother. Her voice, it changed before she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还失去了谁 姐妹 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who else did you lose? A sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个弟弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.10,0:22:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的内心有一种死亡的气息 就像…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a deadness inside her. It's like a--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.52,0:22:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有底的井 将一切吸入\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's like a well with no bottom, just sucking everything in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She wants to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想让所有人死 我感觉到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She wants everyone to die. I felt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在崩溃时说了什么 你听懂了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What she said when she broke, did you understand any of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.03,0:22:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听懂了一些 是古安纳克里昂语 不是通用语\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some, yeah. It's archaic Anacreon, not the common vernacular.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.75,0:22:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说漏嘴了 因为我也听懂了一些话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, she slipped up. Because I understood something too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个我曾在全息影像见过的名字 拉肯柯恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A name I remember from the holos. Larken Keaen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.30,0:22:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在安铎星带纠纷事件时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}During the Anthor Belt dispute,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.01,0:22:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安纳克里昂和狄斯比斯为帝国带去贡礼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anacreon and Thespis brought gifts to the Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.34,0:22:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我族人带的是《洗礼经》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My people's was the Book of Ablut--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.93,0:22:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安纳克里昂的是一把 为其最伟大猎手雕刻的弓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Anacreon's was a bow carved for its greatest hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.85,0:22:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-拉肯柯恩 -意思是 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Larken Keaen. -Meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:22:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉不是什么捡垃圾的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Phara's not just some junker.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是安纳克里昂的大猎手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's the Grand Huntress of Anacreon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.24,0:23:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切动乱到底是谁造成的 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All this unrest, who's responsible for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.20,0:23:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堕落者 这是一个化名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sinkers. A nom de guerre.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.33,0:23:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,77层的热沉室熔化后 那是星桥坠落造成的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After the heat sink meltdown on level 77. It was caused when the Star Bridge fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,35年后 我们仍在处理这件事的余波\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And 35 years later we're still grappling with the aftereffects.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.30,0:23:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大帝的职责就是 处理一堆相互竞争优先级的事项\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The businesses of Empire is a cascade of competing priorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.10,0:23:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和主教团会面时 白昼兄弟将会需要你的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brother Day will need your support while I tend to the conclave.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.27,0:23:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公务太繁多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.56,0:23:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于一个人而言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For one man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.86,0:23:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸运的是我们有三个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fortunately, there are three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.48,0:23:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏事往往成三 你听说了吗 兄弟 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bad tidings also come in threes. Have you heard the news, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.91,0:23:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大角星区有一个通讯浮标断联了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A communications buoy in the Arcturus Sector has come off-line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.91,0:23:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些浮标应该常常断联吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They must go off-line all the time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.95,0:24:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们大概有几千个浮标遍布整个星系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We probably have thousands of them across the galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.33,0:24:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数万个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tens of thousands.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.67,0:24:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只有那个浮标负责外围星域的通讯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But only one that handles communications in the Outer Reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.17,0:24:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有理解此事的严重性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I see that you fail to grasp the significance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.22,0:24:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是端点星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's Terminus.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.14,0:24:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄昏兄弟将哈里谢顿的信徒流放到那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's where Brother Dusk exiled Hari Seldon's followers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.39,0:24:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外围星域、主教团、叛变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Reach. The conclave. Insurgency…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.94,0:24:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看出这一系列事情的规律了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you see a pattern forming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.11,0:24:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给他们看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Show them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.99,0:24:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感知到你们的脆弱后 很快将有其他力量 开始对帝国进行破坏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sensing vulnerability, soon other players will begin to apply downward pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.91,0:24:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河中某个主要的宗教必然会发起煽动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An exhortation from one of the galaxy's major religions is a given.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.66,0:24:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是川陀本地发起的起义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or perhaps a homegrown insurrection here on Trantor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.17,0:24:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果灭亡的速度可以加快 那可以减慢吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the fall can be accelerated, can it not also be slowed?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.84,0:24:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧瞧你现在 兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now look at you, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.05,0:24:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在中央王座上 刚愎自用的样子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So smugly self-assured atop the middle throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.55,0:24:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前会在镜子前练习这个笑容\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I used to practice that smile in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.97,0:25:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 我知道这一幕的结局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Enough. I know how the scene ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.14,0:25:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你领会了其中的教训吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But have you embraced its lessons?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.02,0:25:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透光教 如今堕落者起义了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Luminism. The Sinker insurrection happening now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.10,0:25:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢顿几乎给你列了一份待做事项清单\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seldon all but drew you a to-do list.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.90,0:25:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你却完全无视\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you ignored him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.98,0:25:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他是个江湖骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because he was a charlatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.69,0:25:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有任何新的创造\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You offer nothing new.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.99,0:25:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是一个更嫩的葡萄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just a younger grape…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.49,0:25:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自同一个葡萄藤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}from the same vine,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.12,0:25:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注定酿成同样的酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}destined for the same old bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.04,0:25:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们无法拯救自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't save yourselves…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.21,0:25:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你们能拯救功业 传承后世\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you can save your legacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.84,0:25:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里谢顿已死去多时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hari Seldon is long dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.09,0:25:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是被自己的学徒杀死的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Murdered by his protégé, no less.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.42,0:25:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人是死了 但是阻止得了起义吗 兄弟 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The man was murdered. But what about the movement, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.30,0:25:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈士的影响力往往超越其本身的生命长度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Martyrs tend to have a long half-life.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.19,0:25:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你 我们所看到的是 一个真正的外交危机的开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks to you, we are now staring down the barrel of a genuine diplomatic crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.19,0:25:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该做什么 路易斯 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What was I supposed to do, Lewis?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.24,0:25:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让法拉杀了我 然后对孩子们动手 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let Phara kill me and then move on to the kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.12,0:25:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不该在我不在场的情况下拷问她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You shouldn't have questioned her without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.83,0:26:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应庆幸 我们知道她的身份了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be glad I did. We know who she is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.58,0:26:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有筹码了 可以与她的同伴讨价还价\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have leverage. We can bargain with her people.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.66,0:26:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这个选择让全城陷入暴动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If this choice inflames the city into violence,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.54,0:26:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你成功让我们如此高明地自取灭亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you have achieved elaborate suicide for us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.50,0:26:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里不是说基地会在 第一次危机中存活吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Didn't Hari say the Foundation survives the first crisis?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.96,0:26:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 但正如我曾告诉你的 你是异类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, he did. But, as I've told you before, you are an outlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.84,0:26:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-意思是  -塞佛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Meaning? -Salvor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.05,0:26:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是计算结果不包括你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Meaning that you weren't accounted for.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.72,0:26:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你与穹窿有一种联结\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have a connection with the Vault
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.26,0:26:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那是不可能被预测的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which couldn't have possibly have been predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.60,0:26:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模型中没有你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are not baked into the model.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.14,0:26:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是我不属于上帝的计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're saying I'm not part of God's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.68,0:26:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是心理历史学无法计算个人行为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am saying psychohistory can't account for individuals.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.02,0:26:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你是说我毁了上帝的计划 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you're saying I've destroyed God's plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.60,0:26:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是时候后退一步了 塞佛 -退一步 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-It's time to take a step back, Salvor. -Step back?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.02,0:26:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为基地存在的全部意义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought the whole damn point of the Foundation
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.07,0:26:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在于为难以预料的情况做准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}was preparing for the unthinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.53,0:26:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我要求更多防御武器时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I asked for more defensive weapons,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.70,0:26:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说袭击的可能性极低\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you said the likelihood of an attack seemed remote.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.32,0:26:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我提出进行更多军事训练时 没人回应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I wanted to run more drills, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.95,0:26:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果我们走到这一步 毫无准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So here we are now, not prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.83,0:26:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我是异类 但搞砸计划的不是我 路易斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I might be an outlier, but I'm not the one screwing up the Plan, Lewis.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.26,0:26:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是总督路易斯皮仁恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lewis Pirenne, director.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.38,0:27:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安纳克里昂议事会为什么派最高级的军官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, why would the Anacreon Council send its highest-ranking military officer
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.39,0:27:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到一个帝国哨站 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to an imperial outpost?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.26,0:27:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你们的末日邪教伪装出来的门面吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that what you're pretending your little doomsday cult is?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.93,0:27:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我在这里看不见帝国的影子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I don't see the Empire anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.85,0:27:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只看到学者、劳工和极少的枪械\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All I see are academics, laborers and very few guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.52,0:27:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们破坏了通讯浮标\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You took down the comms buoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.90,0:27:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 我们想暗中行动 避开监控\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course. We wanted to operate in private, away from prying eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.53,0:27:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要明白帝国最终会派人来调查的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have to know the Empire will send someone to investigate eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.45,0:27:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说那就是你的意图 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or is that the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.82,0:27:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这里的女性比男性聪明多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your women are so much sharper than your men.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.87,0:27:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛮族王国被流放了 你们没有理由来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The barbarian kingdoms are exiled. You have no business here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.29,0:27:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“蛮族”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Barbarians."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.54,0:27:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是个用在异类身上的 歧视词语 真是方便\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just a convenient slur for anyone not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.42,0:27:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川陀让我们在这里自生自灭 你的人和我的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trantor left us all here to die. Your people and mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.09,0:27:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不过是以不同的速度灭亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're just dying at different speeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.97,0:27:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基地没有灭亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Foundation isn't dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.39,0:27:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要完成哈里谢顿托付我们的任务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are fulfilling the mission Hari Seldon entrusted us with.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.06,0:27:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢顿也预测到灭亡将会从银河边缘开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seldon also predicted that the fall would begin at the edge of the galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.85,0:27:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这里 -同样的科学计算\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Here. -The same science
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.35,0:27:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在星桥坠落时拯救了帝国宫殿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that saved the Imperial Palace when the Star Bridge fell
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.44,0:27:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也保护着端点市\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}protects Terminus City.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.73,0:27:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说你的能量屏障 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mean your energy barrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.32,0:28:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器的效用取决于使用者的能耐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A weapon's only as good as the man who's wielding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.50,0:28:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯林 你那边情况如何 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kalin, what's your situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.84,0:28:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的人越来越多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's getting pretty crowded over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.84,0:28:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我可能需要支援 -不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I think I need backup. -Not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.18,0:28:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞佛看到十几个人 你是说 到处都是安纳克里昂人 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Salvor saw a dozen. You're telling me we've got Anacreons all over?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.56,0:28:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说我看到他们携带的枪械 足以将整座城夷为平地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm telling you I'm seeing enough guns to take out the whole town.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.81,0:28:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.31,0:28:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们讨论的问题 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The matter we discussed?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.78,0:28:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫阿祖拉欧蒂利 13岁起成为宫殿植物学家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her name is Azura Odili. A palace botanist since the age of 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.95,0:28:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的父亲已身故 生前也是花园的农业生态学家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her father, deceased, was also an agroecologist in the gardens.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.95,0:28:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的母亲创办了一所插花学校 目前已关闭了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her mother founded a school for the ikebana, now closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.62,0:28:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说有什么问题吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said there was a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.75,0:28:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种情况下通常怎么解决问题 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are problems generally solved in this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.80,0:29:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能达到目的就可以 我的职责是让问题消失 大帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any manner that achieves its goal. My job is to eliminate problems, Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.94,0:29:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿祖拉欧戴利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Azura Odili.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.57,0:29:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧迪利 欧德利 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh-dee-lee? Oh-dih-lee?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.65,0:29:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂 大帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dee, Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.82,0:29:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前在我的寝宫外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were outside my chambers earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.32,0:29:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我想知道你认为自己看见了什么 -我什么都没看见 大帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Want to know what you think you saw. -I saw nothing, Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.04,0:29:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我认为你看见了一些东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I believe you saw something.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.87,0:29:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只看见大帝希望我看见的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I only see what Empire wants me to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.12,0:29:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以罢免你的职务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I could have you removed from your station,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.46,0:29:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送你去80层清理热沉室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}sent to scrub the heat sinks on level 80.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.71,0:29:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以对你下狠手 远比这更狠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I could do worse to you. Much worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.05,0:29:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.34,0:29:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大帝 黄昏兄弟让我来请你过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Empire, Brother Dusk has asked me to summon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.93,0:29:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他我马上过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell him I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.22,0:29:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个花圃都移除\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remove this entire bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.35,0:29:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的寝宫 花的香气太浓郁了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From my chambers the smell of the blossoms is overbearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.19,0:29:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-大帝 这种事不需要你… -已经解决了 你走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Empire, you needn't bother with this-- -It's settled. You can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.32,0:30:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狼息叶有助缓解疼痛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wolvesbreath helps with the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.65,0:30:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是带红色条纹的褐绿色叶子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The brownish-green leaves with the red stripe.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.49,0:30:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们能缓解肿胀和淤伤…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They reduce the swelling and bruising--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.07,0:30:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不记得向你征求医疗建议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't recall asking for your medical advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.41,0:30:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪种 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.48,0:30:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尖叶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The pointed leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.62,0:30:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.12,0:30:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狼灵属\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lupi spiritus.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.33,0:30:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是狼息叶 大帝 来自我们的草药园\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wolvesbreath, Empire. From our medicinal garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.91,0:31:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一种镇痛剂和血管舒张药\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's an analgesic and vasodilator.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.79,0:31:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有毒吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it poisonous?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.96,0:31:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 狼息叶可以泡茶或酿药酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Wolvesbreath is used in tea as well as tinctures.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.30,0:31:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它能刺激血管、促进康复…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It stimulates the blood vessels, promotes healing--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.68,0:31:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.64,0:31:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果接下来的几个小时你没死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you're not dead within the next few hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.64,0:31:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就送1公斤到我的寝宫来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}have a kilogram of these sent to my quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.85,0:31:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 大帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course, Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.57,0:31:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷洛弗拉姆 马上回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Laylo Fulham, get your ass back home this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.41,0:31:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会突破吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are they gonna get through?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.49,0:31:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.49,0:31:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都回家去 拜托了 这里不安全 快后退…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go back to your home, people. Please. It's not safe out here. Back up. Back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.46,0:31:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们必须立即离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need to come out here. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.17,0:31:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挺忙的 叶特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kind of busy here, Yate.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.34,0:31:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 但我还是要打给你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know, and I'm still calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.96,0:31:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安纳克里昂军队在东边、西边、南边集结\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've got Anacreon's troops massing from the east, west, south,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.22,0:31:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计北边也有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and presumably the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.51,0:31:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得怎么拿枪吗 老头 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remember how to hold a rifle, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.80,0:31:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枪管对着前方 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Barrel goes forward?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.60,0:31:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在围栏外的多个地点 发现安纳克里昂人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've spotted Anacreons at multiple locations outside the fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.98,0:32:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我去西边 -我们去北边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I'll go west. -We'll head north.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.23,0:32:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不应该离开 路易斯完全不是对手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I shouldn't leave. Lewis is completely overmatched in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.69,0:32:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会照顾他的 我保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll babysit him, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.02,0:32:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.36,0:32:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗 里面有安纳克里昂的头目 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it true? You got some kind of Anacreon chieftain in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.24,0:32:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喝酒了吗 穆勒 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You been drinking, Muller?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.57,0:32:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河系要完蛋了 是吗  哈里的预测成真了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the end of the galaxy, isn't it? Hari's prediction's coming true.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.83,0:32:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听到的是谣言 穆勒 只是一个本地的盗猎者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You got hold of a bad rumor, Muller. Local poacher's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.33,0:32:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们已经到了 对吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're already here, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.79,0:32:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 不如你歇一下吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, why don't you just take a break for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.89,0:32:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.60,0:32:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会伤害你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I won't hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.31,0:32:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just tell me who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.36,0:32:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sal.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.02,0:32:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sal.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.11,0:32:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞 嘿…怎么回事 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sal. Hey, hey. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.70,0:32:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才在川陀的帝国图书馆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was just in the Imperial Library on Trantor.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.74,0:32:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么叫你在那里  -我身处那里 在书架间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-What do you mean you were there? -I mean I was there. In the stacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.37,0:32:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天花板是木制的 还有很多大理石半身像\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The ceiling was wooden, there were all these marble busts.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.58,0:33:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个拿着刀的男孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And there was a boy with a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.79,0:33:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是带我找到安纳克里昂人的那个男孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was the same boy who led me to the Anacreons.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.29,0:33:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是穹窿 我能感觉到它 雨果 它想告诉我些什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the Vault. I can feel it, Hugo. It's trying to tell me something
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.42,0:33:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于安纳克里昂人和这次危机 关于一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about the Anacreons and this crisis. Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.55,0:33:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 听我说 我过去总说 你应该离开这个星球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, listen to me. I've always said you should let this planet shrug you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.47,0:33:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看到你做的事 你竟能感知 法拉内心的想法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But watching you work, where you could sense what Phara was feeling inside…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.81,0:33:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很特别\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that's special.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.40,0:33:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞 别的人不可能做到这点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Other people can't do that, Sal.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.15,0:33:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你有百分之百的信心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have absolute faith in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.07,0:33:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你有百分之百的信心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have absolute faith in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.18,0:33:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们中的谁是统计学大师提沃尔 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who among you is Master Statistician Tivole?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.93,0:34:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大帝 愿明光永不灭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Empire. May the light never dim.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.10,0:34:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿明光永不灭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}May the light never dim.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.73,0:34:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你收到我的征询了 -是 大帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You received my query. -I did, Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.52,0:34:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们尚未得到结果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I can't say yet we have the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.78,0:34:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄昏给你安排这项任务后已经过了多久 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long has it been since Dusk set you to this task?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.41,0:34:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30年 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Three decades?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.61,0:34:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在你那数字陵墓里都忙些什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you do in your mausoleum of calculus
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.87,0:34:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何还没有结果 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if not achieve results?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.96,0:34:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就说进展吧 你有何进展 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Progress, then. What is your progress?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.63,0:34:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们认为哈里谢顿的预测模型 是违背事实的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We believe the-- the predictive models of Hari Seldon to be counterfactual.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.47,0:34:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么说 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you believe this why?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.31,0:34:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在谢顿发表他的异教学说后的35年来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the 35 years since Seldon uttered his heretical proclamations,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.31,0:34:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国扩张了 而不是收缩 无论是以哪个重要的参数…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the Imperium has expanded, rather than contracted, by every critical metric--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.82,0:34:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.07,0:34:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢顿的预言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seldon's prophecies.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.53,0:35:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我说说他的数学计算 这个“序数分析”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Speak to me of his math, this "ordinal analysis."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.24,0:35:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是一幅占卜牌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a spread of fortune teller's cards
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.99,0:35:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢顿选择将其诠释为神旨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which Seldon chose to interpret as divination.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.25,0:35:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在回归模型中发现的证明 并没有证据所支持\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The verification he found in the regression models is unsupported.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.67,0:35:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是近期的种种事件怎么说 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But what of these-- these recent events?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.55,0:35:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主教团 透光教 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The conclave? Luminism?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.93,0:35:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无根据的猜想 同样是模糊而没有证据支持的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Baseless conjecture. Again, vague and unsupported.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.89,0:35:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都能预测到回到正教这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, anyone could predict a return to orthodoxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.48,0:35:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心理历史学只是老人空想出来的研究\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Psychohistory is the fanciful work of an old man's imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.19,0:35:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果它并非老人空想出来的研究 那么是什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If it weren't the fanciful work of an old man's imagination, what then?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.90,0:35:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究最终被证为真实的概率是多少 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is the likelihood that it's all true? Every prophecy?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.70,0:35:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微小得可以忽略 大帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Vanishingly small, Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.95,0:35:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是零\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But not zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.62,0:35:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.83,0:35:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非零 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.63,0:35:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底是什么白痴 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What kind of idiots are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.88,0:35:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一千个帝国数学家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A thousand imperial mathematicians…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.13,0:36:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却理解不了一个人的计算 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}…can't parse the numbers of one man?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.09,0:36:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以银河系中没有任何人有办法 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So there's nothing anyone in the galaxy can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.14,0:36:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你们交出的最佳结果 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that what it is? Is that the best you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.65,0:36:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me. Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.61,0:36:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.25,0:36:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在人生的晚年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the twilight of a man's life…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.13,0:36:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当他的个人历史将近尾声时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}…when his biography is nearly complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.92,0:36:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他开始绝望地想知道他的人生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he grows desperate to know the measure of his days…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.43,0:36:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的声音与前人所有的声音相比结果如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}how his voice compares to the chorus of those who've come before.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.60,0:36:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我重要吗 我的选择是自己做出的吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do I matter? Are my choices my own?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.73,0:36:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的命运是否被看不见的手所左右 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or is my destiny governed by an unseen hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.54,0:37:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白昼兄弟 来为我们送行 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brother Day. Come to see us off?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.71,0:37:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的统计师们来找过我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was paid a visit by your statisticians.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.58,0:37:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的计算结果如此自圆其说 真了不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's remarkable how self-reinforcing their results are.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.59,0:37:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为你最好还是留在川陀处理事务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think it's best that you stay and tend to matters on Trantor.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.84,0:37:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大帝 第一克里昂从未离开过川陀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Empire, a primary Cleon has not left the bosom of Trantor
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.51,0:37:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一脉相承的王朝开始起就没有过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}since the dawn of the Genetic Dynasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.72,0:37:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德默泽尔是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Demerzel is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.60,0:37:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们订立这些规程是有原因的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have these protocols in place for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.48,0:37:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我则认为我们的规程让我们懈怠了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I say our protocols have made us complacent.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.78,0:37:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当年你和我现在一样坐在中央王座上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When you sat on the middle throne, as I do now,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.94,0:37:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨论如何处理安纳克里昂和狄斯比斯时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and were debating what to do about Anacreon and Thespis,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.45,0:37:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们该如何回应 你记得 你当时是怎么说的吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what our response should be, do you remember what you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.12,0:37:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.20,0:37:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛是昨日\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like it was yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.16,0:37:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我七岁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.50,0:37:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们最年长的兄弟认为应该恩赦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our eldest brother had argued for a bout of grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.67,0:38:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你转向我说 “你如何看此事 初升的黎明 ”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You turned to me and said, "What do you think, Ascending Dawn?"
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.71,0:38:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你反对恩赦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I knew you were against grace,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.84,0:38:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想轰炸蛮族王国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that you wanted to bomb the barbarian kingdoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.84,0:38:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我很怕 我大胆说了出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I was scared. And I dared say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.85,0:38:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今我已经不怕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'm not scared anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.10,0:38:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你的统治下 星桥坠落 在那件事的伤疤上 人们掀起起义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On your watch, the Star Bridge fell. And from that scar insurgency was birthed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.07,0:38:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你的统治下 两个世界烧为灰烬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On your watch, two worlds were incinerated
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.57,0:38:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不顾及无辜者或后果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with not a care to innocence or consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.20,0:38:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你的统治下 哈里谢顿和他的信众得以逃离\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On your watch, Hari Seldon and his followers were allowed to flee.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.16,0:38:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把一个因为任性妄为 而四分五裂的帝国交到我手上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have bequeathed me an Empire rent by impulsive action.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.66,0:38:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会重蹈覆辙 在我的统治下不会这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The same will not be said of me. Not on my watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.17,0:38:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将拯救我们的功业\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would save our legacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.67,0:38:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brother…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.01,0:38:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个早已死去的人 阴魂不散 令你无法释怀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you are haunted by the ghost of a man long dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.34,0:38:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都是如此 兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We all are, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.23,0:38:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的统治已经结束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your watch is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.44,0:39:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你将留在川陀 处理你放任不管 而因此恶化的伤口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You will stay on Trantor, tending to the wounds you have allowed to fester.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.32,0:39:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.94,0:39:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把黄昏兄弟的物品送回宫殿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Return Brother Dusk's belongings to the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.62,0:39:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今帝国当然不会因莽撞行事而分崩离析\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Certainly now the Empire will no longer be rent by impulsive action.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.74,0:39:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你召唤我吗 大帝 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You summoned me, Empire?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.95,0:39:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外围星域的一个通讯浮标断联了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A communications buoy has gone dark in the Outer Reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.00,0:40:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带上你的团队去调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take your team and investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.29,0:40:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就去 大帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At once, Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.00,0:40:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多尔文\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dorwin.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.92,0:40:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基地通讯的频率越来越少了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our dispatches from the Foundation have become sporadic.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.67,0:40:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去造访他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pay them a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.84,0:40:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提醒基地 不要对帝国有所隐瞒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And remind the Foundation that Empire will not be kept in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.87,0:41:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那是… -情况不太妙 是吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Is that, uh-- -Doesn't look good, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.02,0:41:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里由谁指挥 路易斯还是你  还是玩硬币的守卫者 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who is in charge here, Lewis? You? Or is it the Warden with the coin tricks?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.10,0:41:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她似乎让情况变得复杂了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because it seems she's managed to complicate matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.52,0:41:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-让我说清楚 猎手柯恩 -大猎手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Let me be clear, Huntress Keaen-- -Grand Huntress.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.94,0:41:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们面临危机的唯一原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The only reason we have a crisis
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.57,0:41:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们擅自入侵帝国的私人领域\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is because you trespassed on the Emperor's personal domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.11,0:41:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果塞佛当时带我去塔那边 把我要的东西给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If only Salvor had taken me to the tower and given me what I'd wanted,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.41,0:41:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们早都离开这个星球了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we'd already be off-planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.12,0:42:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们慢速舰上的模组 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The module from our slow ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.70,0:42:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的人又不会用它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not as if your people have any use for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.71,0:42:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们已经困在端点星了 帝国确保这一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're marooned on Terminus. The Empire made sure of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.38,0:42:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lewis.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.63,0:42:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们为何需要模组 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why do you need it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.13,0:42:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我族人在科技上极其匮乏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My people are technologically bankrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.42,0:42:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要灭亡了 总督\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're dying, Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.84,0:42:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从帝国让我们的大气层燃烧后 我们一直苦苦挣扎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have been ever since the Empire set our atmosphere on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.43,0:42:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一个并非我们犯下的罪行 一半人口失去生命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Half our population lost for a crime that we were innocent of.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.35,0:42:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你们不同 我们有飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unlike you, we have ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.27,0:42:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能够离开被摧毁的世界 寻找另一个恒星系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can leave our poisoned world, find another star system.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.94,0:42:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只需要在虚空中导航的工具\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If only we had the means to navigate the void.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.19,0:42:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果支援你们 帝国会摧毁我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Empire would crush us for assisting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.99,0:42:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这是在逼你出手相助 总督\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're forcing your hand, Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.74,0:42:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们已经没什么可失去的了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because we have nothing left to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.57,0:42:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无法和一个愿意将棋盘烧毁的人下棋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't play chess with someone who's willing to set the board on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.79,0:42:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是某种高射炮吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that some kind of flak cannon?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.92,0:42:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们以为那能突破围栏 那就是在浪费时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wasting their time if they think that's gonna penetrate the fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.59,0:42:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切都不对劲 法拉应该更高明的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}None of this feels right. Phara is smarter than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.13,0:42:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们摧毁了通讯浮标 他们是有备而来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They took out the comms buoy, and they came in prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.63,0:43:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的策略比我们想的大 但我却看不出到底是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a larger strategy here, and I am missing it somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.39,0:43:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如我乘飞船离开 去其他星球求助 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if I take my ship, make a run for the stars, get help?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.72,0:43:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…你还没进入轨道 就会被他们从空中击落\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no. They'd shoot you out of the sky before you ever made it into orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.14,0:43:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后悔没在还来得及的时候离开了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Regretting you didn't bug out when you had the chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.98,0:43:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这辈子做的傻事多了去了 塞佛哈定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Done a lot of foolish things in my life, Salvor Hardin.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.73,0:43:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪在你身边不是其中之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sticking by your side is not one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.90,0:43:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史上最佳男仆从\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Best manservant ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.62,0:43:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹窿并非出自安纳克里昂之手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Vault isn't Anacreon…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.04,0:43:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是外星生物建的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or alien at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.17,0:43:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它一定与哈里有关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's gotta be connected to Hari.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.71,0:43:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.80,0:43:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我昏迷时看到的画面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because the vision I saw when I blacked out,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.30,0:43:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是川陀星 在哈里的图书馆 有个男孩拿刀指着我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it was on Trantor in Hari's library, with a boy holding a knife on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.72,0:43:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许这是在警告我们远离它 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if it was a warning to stay away?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.64,0:43:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果路易斯是对的呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if Lewis is right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.22,0:43:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如他所说的 我是异类 横冲直撞、四处捣乱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm an outlier, just like he says, barging around, knocking things over,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.44,0:43:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞砸了谢顿的计划 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}screwing up Seldon's plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.81,0:43:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞佛 如果你就是谢顿的计划呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Salvor, what if you are Seldon's plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.57,0:43:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,个人的命运将永远是一个谜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The fate of one individual will always remain a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.36,0:44:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守卫者 还记得我的承诺吗  夷平你的城市 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remember my promise, Warden? Razing your city to the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.83,0:44:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一群人的行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the movements of masses,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.87,0:44:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化的兴起与消亡 因果与世界…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the rise and falls of cultures, causes and worlds…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.25,0:44:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于这些问题 哈里谢顿早已解开谜底\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These were answers Hari Seldon had long since unriddled.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.09,0:44:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.46,0:44:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如其名字所描述的 这场终结的开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the beginning of the end, as befitting its name,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.34,0:44:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在端点星上发生了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}took place on Terminus.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.30,0:45:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字幕翻译：易晗